flowchart TD
    Citizen[Citizen] --> Intake[Report Life Event]
    Intake --> Interpret[Intake Agent Interprets]
    Interpret --> Programs[Identify Programs]
    Programs --> Eval[Evaluate Each Program]
    Eval --> Explain[Generate 3-Level Explanation]
    Explain --> Review[Flag for Caseworker]
    Review --> Citizen2[Citizen notified]
    Citizen2 --> Human[Caseworker Confirms]
